title: The Rift looking for d5+ jg and more staff

embed.description: Step up your game with a modern voice & text chat app. Crystal clear voice, multiple server and channel support, mobile apps, and more. Get your free server now!

body: we are looking for a d5+ jg to play in one of the amateur teams we have aswell as staff to help running tournaments that will be sponsored by ocs and opl teams most likely.. aswell as helping with the team. we are also looking to build a community around it so come join if you want somewhere to play with your friends
